snippet.title: Wizard (Evercade - Atari Collection 2) Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage from the Atari Collection 2 cartridge for the Evercade.

Originally captured for use in an Evercade video on my main channel, this is the original footage without commentary.

I more than likely used save states, but all of the menu navigation has been edited out.

Game footage was captured from an Evercade console via HDMI output.   


The Crow Continuum YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/thecrowcontinuum
